## Installation

```
npm i
```

### Create a launch.json file

To enable VS Code debugging, create a `launch.json` file in `.vscode` directory with the following content:

```
{
    "version": "0.2.0",
    "configurations": [
        {
            "type": "node",
            "request": "launch",
            "name": "Launch Program",
            "program": "${file}",
            "preLaunchTask": "tsc: build - tsconfig.json"
        }
    ]
}
```


## Running in dev mode

```
npm start <day>
```

Example:

```
npm start 1
```
